<p><a name="Interwar_years" id="Interwar_years"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Blitzkrieg&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Interwar years">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Interwar years</span></h2>
<p><a name="Reichswehr" id="Reichswehr"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Blitzkrieg&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Reichswehr">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Reichswehr</span></h3>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Bundesarchiv_Bild_102-12140,_Verfassungsfeier,_Ehrenkompanie_der_Reichswehr.jpg" class="image" title="President Hindenburg attends a guard of honor of the Reichswehr, 1926."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/45/Bundesarchiv_Bild_102-12140%2C_Verfassungsfeier%2C_Ehrenkompanie_der_Reichswehr.jpg/180px-Bundesarchiv_Bild_102-12140%2C_Verfassungsfeier%2C_Ehrenkompanie_der_Reichswehr.jpg" width="180" height="128" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
